{{rfc|date=June 2006}}

Short for nucleus as it relates to the small beginnings of a beehive. The term is used for a baited box (usually with honey) that bees can enter not leave. The nuc is used to capture a swarm or nest of bees for removal and transport.
==English==

==={{initialism}}===
'''NUC'''

# '''Neutral Unit of Construction''', a [[fictitious]] [[currency]] used in the calculation of international air fares.

